'''Geridard Convalescent Center''' was an expensive retirement home on [[Geridard]] that provided life care. Sentients could apply to become a resident with a deposit in advance.

[[Augusta I'att]] was to be admitted, though her execution at the hands of [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Eisen Kerioth|Kerioth]] prevented that.

